    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-01-12T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-01-12T04:00:00-05:00" n="16"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d16">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/12074: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Tsingtao</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sokobin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tsingtao</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-01-12T17:00:00+08:00"
                            >January 12, 1938—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 13—1:20 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Complete peace and order naturally prevail. Japanese authorities have informed
                    Commissioner of Customs there will be no interference with operation of Maritime
                    Customs but naturally he must recognize that new regime exists and that further
                    examination will be worked out. Chinese post office also operating normally with
                    the exception of Japanese censors.</p>
                <p>Proclamation issued by Japanese Commander-in-Chief of naval landing forces
                    advised international populace to continue their peaceful pursuits but they must
                    strictly observe and obey Japanese military orders and proclamations.</p>
                <p>Sent to Peiping, Hankow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sokobin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
